MODIFICATIONS:

This fork includes the following significant changes from the original:

- Updated Go from v1.12 to v1.24
- Updated all Prometheus dependencies to latest versions
- Added comprehensive test suite (80% coverage)
- Modernized CI/CD with GitHub Actions security best practices
- Added Trivy vulnerability scanning
- Added CodeQL static analysis
- Simplified build system (removed promu dependency)
- Multi-platform Docker support (amd64, arm64)
- Fixed all known CVEs

See CHANGELOG.md for detailed modification history.
